item.title: About us
item.description: IX is a small Computer/Electronics non profit organization that houses in Stockholm. Email You can send emails to the board at ix@ufs.se. Phone There’s a phone in UFS that you can call to. If you want to reach IX it’s best to call during Monday evenings. The number there is +46 8-10 77 00. Postal address To send letters to IX, you can do it to: IX C/O Unga Forskare Stockholm Box 8006 104 20 Stockholm Sweden Visit us IX houses at UFS place on Mondays from around 18:00.
